INSERT INTO reviews VALUE('Ziye Zhang',5,1,1,'Great and informative class! I took this class with Professor Caruthers, and he was very thoughtful and considerate of students. The workload is not a lot and not stressful at all. You get to read 3 books that are very interesting and relevant. This class gave me a lot of insight to developing evidence-based policy especially as a non-CRP major. This also counts as a technical elective for ENG majors.','CRP 3270',343);
