INSERT INTO reviews VALUE('Antonio DiTommaso',5,3,3,'I took this class in Spring 2020, which was a rollercoaster term. The professors adjusted the class as best as they could with what they had. Both Dr. DiTommaso and Dr. Losey are passionate about the course and strive to have activities that allow the students to learn. We had a semester-long research project in small groups (that got adjusted during COVID) which is a large part of the class but most assignments are labs (and lab reports) and preparing for the exams (which are all short-answer questions). I enjoyed this class and learned a lot from it, even with COVID changing the atmosphere.','ENTOM 4440',1318);
