INSERT INTO reviews VALUE('Nicolas Buchon',4,2,2,'I took the class in the fall with Buchon, Helmann, and Selvaraj. The first few lectures were reviews of high school biology but the course content eventually got more interesting. My main complaint about the class is that we were required to watch online video lectures, which got tedious when I also went to in-person \"lecture discussions\". The workload is fairly light, and not much is required for labs. There was a generous curve for grading.','BIOG 1440',921);
