INSERT INTO reviews VALUE('Paul Friedland',5,3,3,'I really loved this class! Professor Friedland and Professor Verhoeven are both great lecturers; all lectures dealt with very different trials so it was really interesting to see how the professors connected them through various themes. Weekly readings were very relevant to the topics discussed in class so even if they were difficult to decipher or long at times, they were always very interesting and useful in the end.  The essays were manageable and I especially liked the presentation option of the final project; it allowed for some creativity that I hadn''t experienced in other classes.','HIST 1600',1334);
